      <title>恐慌席卷巴西市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-18/panic-sweeps-brazilian-markets-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资者对巴西政府遏制日益加深的财政危机的能力失去了信心。交易员纷纷对冲主权债务违约的风险，该国货币、股票和债券均遭遇抛售。彭博社拉丁美洲执行编辑 Crayton Harrison 在“与 Francine Lacqua 一起脉搏”节目中讨论了这一问题。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-18/panic-sweeps-brazilian-markets-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 10:31:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
